What we have surmised so far is, maintaining the old lamps is tedious and time-consuming. The cost of rewiring the current system is prohibitive. Installing new lights would eliminate the charm of the community.Yet, public safety is the main reason for streetlights. Not charm. If the old ones are failing, what is the plan to keep residents safe? Loma Portal is a short walk for unsavory characters who might use the cover of darkness to their advantage.
